document.full_text: tsunami warnings have been lifted for some densely populated asia pacific countries previously thought to be at risk after a huge earthquake that hit japan friday, the u.s. pacific tsunami warning center (ptwc) and national officials said.
document.title: some pacific tsunami alerts lifted after japan quake
